I hated seeing my sister's sad face because of me.

21
00:01:40,067 --> 00:01:43,100
But, I'm glad my little brother is taking the medicine well.

22
00:01:45,733 --> 00:01:48,667
Yeah, I like taking medicine.

23
00:01:49,733 --> 00:01:50,833
That's a relief.

24
00:02:01,033 --> 00:02:04,900
So, I just said everything was good.

25
00:02:06,833 --> 00:02:09,667
I'm interested in you,
so please give me your number.

26
00:02:09,667 --> 00:02:12,100
Yes.

27
00:02:12,100 --> 00:02:13,567
I like all of you.

28
00:02:13,567 --> 00:02:16,300
I thought it would be okay
if I said I like everything.

29
00:02:31,933 --> 00:02:33,400
Did you cheat on my friends?

30
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,333
Because of you, Min Hee and Ji Soo…

31
00:02:36,367 --> 00:02:39,900
Have you ever thought about
the feelings of someone who likes you?

32
00:02:41,767 --> 00:02:42,700
What?

33
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:46,900
At least my friends sincerely liked you.

34
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:47,933
Sincerely.

35
00:02:49,767 --> 00:02:50,800
And, you know what?

36
00:02:51,567 --> 00:02:54,133
You're the one who doesn't know the sincerity.

37
00:02:54,133 --> 00:02:56,367
You're not able to like someone.

38
00:02:56,367 --> 00:03:00,400
So in the end, you won't be loved by anyone.

39
00:03:01,867 --> 00:03:02,933
Understand?

40
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,033
Yeah.

41
00:03:06,133 --> 00:03:07,667
Don't regret it later.

42
00:03:08,933 --> 00:03:10,200
You piece of crap.

43
00:03:17,867 --> 00:03:21,900
After that, I continued…

44
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,100
- You.
- You won't.

45
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:25,033
- Won't.
- Be loved by anyone.

46
00:03:25,033 --> 00:03:26,933
You won't be loved by anyone.

47
