00:20:59,433 --> 00:21:00,967
I was so embarrassed.

273
00:21:02,633 --> 00:21:04,567
It felt like all my feelings of liking

274
00:21:05,767 --> 00:21:07,167
had been discovered.

275
00:21:12,267 --> 00:21:13,967
But the really strange thing is

276
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:17,267
I thought it might be a good excuse

277
00:21:19,867 --> 00:21:23,067
since my feelings for him

278
00:21:23,067 --> 00:21:24,467
were discovered anyway.

279
00:21:25,033 --> 00:21:27,900
Either I completely push him away,

280
00:21:27,900 --> 00:21:29,000
or,

281
00:21:30,367 --> 00:21:32,200
I completely like him.

282
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,867
And he is?

283
00:21:35,433 --> 00:21:36,667
Jeong Gi Seop.

284
00:21:42,633 --> 00:21:44,900
Why do all the people I like

285
00:21:44,900 --> 00:21:47,167
like Jeong Gi Seop?

286
00:21:47,167 --> 00:21:49,767
There's someone else?

287
00:21:49,767 --> 00:21:50,767
Yeah.

288
00:21:51,567 --> 00:21:53,867
One of Jeong Gi Seop's ex-girlfriends.

289
00:21:53,867 --> 00:21:56,900
I also made this ideal type note
because of her.

290
00:22:02,500 --> 00:22:03,767
[Jeong Gi Seop XXX]

291
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:06,467
Maybe our ideal type note…

292
00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:10,100
Don't you think it was made to dislike someone,

293
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:13,633
but not to like someone?

294
00:22:16,100 --> 00:22:18,667
Yeah, that's right.

295
00:22:18,667 --> 00:22:20,400
I roughly expected it.

296
00:22:22,133 --> 00:22:24,433
But I couldn't help it.

297
00:22:24,433 --> 00:22:26,433
- What?
- I just…

298
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:30,333
I just got revenge on Jeong Gi Seop.

299
00:22:30,333 --> 00:22:31,633
What revenge?

300
00:22:32,467 --> 00:22:34,833
Well, it might not be a big deal to him.

301
00:22:34,833 --> 00:22:38,167
I was just so annoyed with Jeong Gi Seop

302
00:22:38,167 --> 00:22:40,000
that I went to argue with him.

303
00:22:41,867 --> 00:22:44,367
Actually, it's not his fault.

304
00:22:44,367 --> 00:22:48,133
Even though it was my fault
for not being able to approach the girl I liked.

305
00:22:49,767 --> 00:22:51,400
Well…

306
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:54,067
I guess I just didn't want to admit it.

307
00:22:54,067 --> 00:22:55,233
No.

308
00:22:57,133 --> 00:22:58,433
I think it's annoying.

309
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:02,633
He usually makes me angry a lot.

310
00:23:03,233 --> 00:23:06,600
Right. It's really kind of annoying, right?

311
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,733
It's the worst.

312
00:23:07,733 --> 00:23:09,267
I know.

313
00:23:09,267 --> 00:23:10,800
There's nothing I can do.

314
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:13,867
Still,

315
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:17,300
I like him.

316
00:23:22,967 --> 00:23:24,133
Do you know

317
00:23:25,700 --> 00:23:28,000
strangely enough, I'm very honest with you?

318
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,467
Me too.

319
00:23:29,467 --> 00:23:32,733
I think it's almost the first time
I've told someone

320
00:23:32,733 --> 00:23:35,167
how I feel like this.

321
00:23:35,167 --> 00:23:37,833
Are you going to do the same to Jeong Gi Seop?

322
00:23:37,833 --> 00:23:39,500
Are you seriously

323
00:23:39,500 --> 00:23:40,967
going to confess to him?

324
00:24:10,700 --> 00:24:13,067
Oh? It's snow.

325
00:24:13,067 --> 00:24:14,300
It's snowing.

326
00:24:19,100 --> 00:24:20,767
Was it going to snow today?

327
00:24:20,767 --> 00:24:21,833
It's snow?

328
00:24:23,433 --> 00:24:24,467
First snow.

329
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:31,833
It's so pretty.

330
00:25:10,967 --> 00:25:11,967
Wait.

331
00:25:12,867 --> 00:25:14,167
Look.

332
00:25:14,167 --> 00:25:16,167
The first snow hasn't fallen yet.

333
00:25:16,167 --> 00:25:17,200
[First snow is expected to be later
than usual, may be later than January]

334
00:25:17,200 --> 00:25:19,333
If you recognize me on the first snowy day,

335
00:25:19,333 --> 00:25:21,400
I will become your perfect ideal type.

336
00:25:22,333 --> 00:25:23,833
And Kim Jin Woo.

337
00:25:23,833 --> 00:25:25,733
I have one more claim to make to you.

338
00:25:26,467 --> 00:25:27,467
I won't

339
00:25:28,633 --> 00:25:30,500
leave you alone until the end.

340
00:25:32,667 --> 00:25:35,700
Are you seriously going to confess to him?

341
00:25:43,133 --> 00:25:44,200
Jeong Gi Seop.

342
00:25:51,167 --> 00:25:52,167
Jeong Gi Seop?

343
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:15,067
I failed.

344
00:26:15,067 --> 00:26:16,400
I'll stop it now.

345
00:26:19,333 --> 00:26:21,367
I'm sorry for bothering you for so long.

346
00:26:35,333 --> 00:26:36,567
It's over now.
